description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of New Jersey, which features the end of the lake trip and a second birthday for Evan. He also talks Meghan and Harry, and on The Real Housewives of Dallas, Dee returns to save the show and a shaman/hair dresser shows up.


RHOD Recap: 20:50ish
